<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
	<title>@ViewData["Title"] - Digital Viagem</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.6.3/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-UHRtZLI+pbxtHCWp1t77Bi1L4ZtiqrqD80Kn4Z8NTSRyMA2Fd33n5dQ8lWUE00s/" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-toggleable-sm border-bottom box-shadow mb-3 navbar-color">
			<div class="container ">
				<a class="navbar-brand text-white" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Digital Viagem</a>
				<button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-collapse" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
						aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
					<span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
				</button>
				<div class="navbar-collapse collapse d-sm-inline-flex justify-content-between">
					<ul class="navbar-nav flex-grow-1">
						<li class="nav-item">
							<a class="nav-link text-white" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Home</a>
						</li>
						<li class="nav-item">
							<a class="nav-link text-white" asp-area="" asp-controller="Destinos" asp-action="Viagem">Destinos</a>
						</li>
						<li class="nav-item">
							<a class="nav-link text-white" asp-area="" asp-controller="Cliente" asp-action="Index">Clientes</a>
						</li>
						<li class="nav-item">
							<a class="nav-link text-white" asp-area="" asp-controller="Viagens" asp-action="Index">Viagens</a>
						</li>
						<li class="nav-item">
							<img class="ml-3 iconcart img-fluid" src="https://i.ibb.co/1QK1YLD/63007shoppingcart-109353.png" alt="Generic placeholder image">
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</nav>
	</header>
	<div class="container">
		<main role="main" class="pb-3">
			@RenderBody()
		</main>
	</div>
	<!--Rodapé-->
	<footer class="bg-dark text-white">
		<div class="container-fluid py-4">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-2">
					<ul class="nav flex-column">
						<li class="nav-link"><a href="#">Home</a></li>
						<li class="nav-link"><a href="#">Sobre</a></li>
						<li class="nav-link"><a href="#">Contato</a></li>
						<li class="nav-link"><a href="#">Suporte</a></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="col-5">
					<form>
						<div class="form-group">
							<label for="exampleInputPassword1">Nome:</label>
							<input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputName" placeholder="Seu nome completo">
						</div>
						<div class="form-group">
							<label for="exampleInputEmail1">E-mail:</label>
							<input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail1" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Seu email">
							<small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">Nunca vamos compartilhar seu email, com ninguém.</small>
						</div>
						<div class="form-group">
							<label for="exampleFormControlTextarea1">Mensagem:</label>
							<textarea class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlTextarea1" rows="3"></textarea>
						</div>
						<button type="submit" onclick="funcaoAlert()" class="btn btn-primary">Enviar</button>
						
					</form>
				</div>
				<div class="col-4 ">
					<img class="float-left figure-img img-fluid rounded" id="img-rodape" src="https://s2.glbimg.com/M_L8jcZdEmkiFeJZBpd1XHiIXSg=/1080x608/top/smart/http://g.glbimg.com/og/gs/gsat4/f/thumbs/materia/2015/03/11/info-calculadora-viagem.jpg" />
					<p class="textorodape">
						Somos a Digital Viagem e faremos acontecer aquela sua viagem que antes nem parecia possível, mas agora é. Nascemos da ideia de que viajar é para todos e é transformador. Venha com a gente!
					</p>
					<ul class="nav">
						<li class="nav-link"><i class="fab fa-facebook fa-3x "></i></li>
						<li class="nav-link"><i class="fab fa-instagram fa-3x"></i></li>
						<li class="nav-link"><i class="fab fa-twitter fa-3x"></i></li>
						<li class="nav-link"><i class="fab fa-whatsapp fa-3x"></i></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="text-center" style="background-color: #333; padding: 20px;">
			&copy 2021 Copyright: <a href="#">Digital Viagem</a>
		</div>
	</footer>
	<script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
	<script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
	@await RenderSectionAsync("Scripts", required: false)
</body>
</html>
